<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Connection Lost | BioBrain</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2dd4bf; /* BioBrain Teal */
            --dark: #020617;
            --slate: #1e293b;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--dark);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Animated Grid Background */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90px, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            transform: perspective(500px) rotateX(45deg);
            animation: move 20s linear infinite;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @keyframes move {
            from { transform: perspective(500px) rotateX(45deg) translateY(0); }
            to { transform: perspective(500px) rotateX(45deg) translateY(50px); }
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .icon-box {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .fa-atom {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            animation: rotate 10s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 0.8;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        p {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .action-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.3);
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            background: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-filled {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--dark);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Scanline effect */
        .scanline {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.1);
            z-index: 20;
            animation: scan 4s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes scan {
            0% { top: 0%; }
            100% { top: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="scanline"></div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="icon-box">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-atom"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Synapse Disconnected</h2>
        <p>The neural pathway to this resource has been severed. Our systems are unable to locate the requested data packet.</p>
        
        <div class="action-bar">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-filled">Re-Initialize</a>
            <a href="/support" class="btn">Diagnostics</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>